" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成蟲勁到令大仙出盡全力"},{"pid":"1e35b09e1e583b5bb59915e4bf99359ad55b5690","tid":753781,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53133abcc64ceb891818c443154c5181b4e98fd","tid":753781,"uid":8858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4816e4ae3f6311b9c4ae7a6155be33a3e4a7cf8","tid":753781,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好準"},{"pid":"3905561fdb6de4d0fef4d9e5ade3d76e09500cff","tid":753781,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24fe0097ee90d3d3d54056b530124223d7a7779","tid":753781,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:08:24.000Z","msg":"準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8955b93386f4e915172347e2caad61228f2a32","tid":753781,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52940085037850587f872eddd500457ca6fe5a1c","tid":753781,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180214/photo/bkn-20180214000231238-0214_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180214055141\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180214000231238-0214_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180214055141&h=03fd3528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國近年積極推動「一帶一路」，着力建立完善的跨國經濟帶，又牽頭籌建亞洲基礎設施投資銀行(亞投行)，加強與亞洲及西方國家或地區的合作，獲得各國響應，中國國力以至對全球的影響力日益增強。不過，黃大仙靈籤卻預測狗年中國運勢未如理想，仙師在中國整體運勢及中外關係兩方面，連續賜予兩支下下籤，堪輿學家預示中國在新一年將遇上「多矛盾、多糾紛」，其中與美國的關係更如「打敗仗」，經濟有機會因而走下坡。 <br />\n<br />\n黃大仙師為中國整體運勢批示靈籤「孔子聞衛樂」，屬下下籤，籤文謂：「鄭衛之音不忍聽，淫風敗俗國將傾」，意指鄭國及衛國的音樂誨淫敗俗，聽得多國家早晚滅亡。黃大仙解籤樓堪輿學家佛隱居士指，籤文含意若套在中國內部運勢，可解作今年推動的國策，縱然領導層滿意，但民間卻有怨言，也預示今年內地或有零星內亂，提醒藏獨疆獨分子可能會發動襲擊搞破壞。治安方面，涉及大城市的色情和毒品罪案增加，無論內亂或罪案，中國政府都要如孔子訓斥般，阻於微燃時。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180214/photo/bkn-20180214000231238-0214_00822_001_04p.jpg?20180214055141\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180214000231238-0214_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20180214055141&h=b3c06778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中外關係以中美關係最備受關注。中美兩國關係錯綜複雜，爭拗與合作並存，近年兩國構建新型大國關係或建設性戰略夥伴關係，朝着合作共贏的方向發展。但美國重返西太平洋的戰略部署，令中國東海和南海局勢變得波譎雲詭，外部勢力圍堵中國的行動從未息止，擦槍走火的危機未散，而籤文預示中國一旦面對與美國的衝突會「打敗仗」。居士不諱言，即使未必真「打仗」，軍事威嚇亦會斷續發生，甚至會有因聲稱領土領海被侵入而引發的零星「肢體碰撞」，而中國則會落入下風。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，中國經濟過去數年整體向上，在國際間佔重要席位，但外憂令其在狗年有機會呈現走下坡之勢。居士坦言，國際間的爭拗對中國「百害而無一利」，連經濟亦無可避免會大受影響，「唔得穩陣」，今年甚至可能一改增長強勢，開始逆轉。總括而言，中外關係今年爭拗多，「有排頭痕」。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180214/bkn-20180214000231238-0214_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180214%2Fbkn-20180214000231238-0214_00822_001.html&d=J2irMVgUbvGxlRYH3ktlev1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=26519300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180214/bkn-20180214000231238-0214_00822_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/151802_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F151802_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b691fb20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香夭啊，留名邊個獨臂"},{"pid":"49ed4998c5f5671b0b0a31a97ddf2a2cef581051","tid":753781,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:41:14.000Z","msg":"上一代金句：有時有啲嘢唔到你唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70615d45807fb3749bcbeb28f04a8019ab03522d","tid":753781,"uid":17263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:41:56.000Z","msg":"好擔心大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2c2db3df6a6a4b9e13f9b92dcf68f6b37df81d","tid":753781,"uid":141295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺　<br />\n蒼天有眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dcc7cc52fc7bbb521f62a24eb3f2760ef105a4","tid":753781,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}